pgDev.bukkit.DisguiseCraft
Class Disguise

java.lang.Object
  pgDev.bukkit.DisguiseCraft.Disguise

public class Disguise
extends Object

This is the class for every disguise object. It contains the functions for creating, editing, and sending disguises.

Author:
PG Dev Team (Devil Boy, Tux2)
